SUMMARY:Swordes
LOCATION:The Casbah
DESCRIPTION:Underground electro/hyperpop nonconformist\n\nCutting her teeth
  within the Brooklyn warehouse rave scenes\, Swordes makes - in her own wo
 rds - human music for humans.\nThe result is a headstrong hardware-only ap
 proach to composing\, producing and performing\, juxtaposing cutesy hyper 
 pop elements with gloomier\, gnarlier 80s electronica influences. Bubblegu
 m\, rainbows\, fire and gasoline: Swordes brings a club-friendly pop exorc
 ism that pierces like the sharpest of blades.
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
