SUMMARY:supermodel*
LOCATION:The Casbah
DESCRIPTION:Catchy & distinctive genre-blender with DIY-ethos\n\nUS artist 
 Frankie Beanie's ground rules for his solo-project supermodel*: don't try 
 and be cool\, nick everything\, keep it lowercase\, don't overthink\, alwa
 ys talk about fight club. It translates to fun\, thrifty songs that channe
 l MF Doom as much as LCD Soundsystem. Beanie’s frank\, observational lyr
 ics draw partly from his experiences as an American living in the UK\, com
 plete with Be Kind Rewind-esque homages to Jamiroquai and Fatboy Slim. Eff
 ortlessly charming\, unpolished and yeah\, actually pretty damn cool.
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
