SUMMARY:Tramhaus (DJ Set)
LOCATION:The Casbah
DESCRIPTION:Casbah DJ set by Rotterdam's rowdiest band\n\nTramhaus's snowba
 lling success from Rotterdam's lively underground to one of Europe's great
 est livebands has been downright inspiring.\nAnd in that journey\, its mem
 bers have amassed a great deal of inspiration themselves from music both l
 ocal and far across the world. A breadth of influences and favorites disti
 lled down to an energetic DJ set at their familiar stomping grounds The Ca
 sbah.
